price stability: do we need a technical way to make it easier to sign contracts between each and each participant, or is it enough to let the network grow organically? It may be easier to consider this system in context of the "order book" currency(above). Person A buys something from person B, means B extends credit to A. Now B can also hand A a signed letter acknowledging his debt...



